Inflection

Example: lezen -> las		Type:					Rules:

Condition: past simple, first person, singular

lezen
↓
db: l{$1:e}zen				Simple Inflection 		Trim_end: -en, base-modification: {$1['e'->'a']}
↓				     
laz							Inflection script		pseudo code
							"Ortography"
							scope: global						
													if wordsEnds with -az
														do replace -az with -as
													else
														do nothing
↓
las


Example 2: zijn -> was

Condition: past simple (table), singular (heading), first person (row)		

zijn						
↓
db: zijn,			Simple Inflection 				suffix: -s
stem(past): wa-		from irregular stem
↓							
was
